<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Java Cơ Bản on LLHISME'S Blog</title><link>https://llhisme.github.io/tags/java-c%C6%A1-b%E1%BA%A3n/</link><description>Recent content in Java Cơ Bản on LLHISME'S Blog</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>vi</language><managingEditor>lamlyhao453@gmail.com (Lâm Lý Hào)</managingEditor><webMaster>lamlyhao453@gmail.com (Lâm Lý Hào)</webMaster><lastBuildDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://llhisme.github.io/tags/java-c%C6%A1-b%E1%BA%A3n/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Java Cơ Bản #5: Vòng Lặp - For, While và Do-While</title><link>https://llhisme.github.io/post/java/java-co-ban-5/</link><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>lamlyhao453@gmail.com (Lâm Lý Hào)</author><guid>https://llhisme.github.io/post/java/java-co-ban-5/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="vòng-lặp-là-gì"&gt;Vòng lặp là gì?&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Vòng lặp&lt;/strong&gt; (Loop) cho phép chúng ta thực hiện một đoạn code nhiều lần mà không cần viết lại. Giống như khi bạn cần in 100 số từ 1 đến 100, thay vì viết 100 dòng &lt;code&gt;System.out.println()&lt;/code&gt;, bạn chỉ cần dùng vòng lặp.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Java có 3 loại vòng lặp chính:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;For loop&lt;/strong&gt;: Biết trước số lần lặp&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;While loop&lt;/strong&gt;: Lặp khi điều kiện còn đúng&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Do-while loop&lt;/strong&gt;: Thực hiện ít nhất 1 lần, sau đó kiểm tra điều kiện&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="1-vòng-lặp-for"&gt;1. Vòng lặp For&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="cú-pháp-cơ-bản"&gt;Cú pháp cơ bản:&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code class="language-java" data-lang="java"&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="k"&gt;for&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;khởi_tạo&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;điều_kiện&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;cập_nhật&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="c1"&gt;// Code thực hiện trong mỗi lần lặp&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="2-vòng-lặp-while"&gt;2. Vòng lặp While&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="cú-pháp"&gt;Cú pháp:&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code class="language-java" data-lang="java"&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="k"&gt;while&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;điều_kiện&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="c1"&gt;// Code thực hiện khi điều kiện đúng&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="c1"&gt;// Cần có code để thay đổi điều kiện, tránh vòng lặp vô hạn&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="3-vòng-lặp-do-while"&gt;3. Vòng lặp Do-While&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="cú-pháp-1"&gt;Cú pháp:&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code class="language-java" data-lang="java"&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="k"&gt;do&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="c1"&gt;// Code thực hiện ít nhất 1 lần&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="k"&gt;while&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;điều_kiện&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;);&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description></item><item><title>Java Cơ Bản #4: Cấu Trúc Điều Khiển - If/Else và Switch</title><link>https://llhisme.github.io/post/java/java-co-ban-4/</link><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>lamlyhao453@gmail.com (Lâm Lý Hào)</author><guid>https://llhisme.github.io/post/java/java-co-ban-4/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="cấu-trúc-điều-khiển-là-gì"&gt;Cấu trúc điều khiển là gì?&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cấu trúc điều khiển&lt;/strong&gt; cho phép chương trình đưa ra quyết định và thực hiện các hành động khác nhau dựa trên điều kiện. Giống như trong cuộc sống, chúng ta thường phải đưa ra quyết định: &amp;ldquo;Nếu trời mưa thì mang ô, nếu không thì không cần&amp;rdquo;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="1-câu-lệnh-if"&gt;1. Câu lệnh If&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="cú-pháp-cơ-bản"&gt;Cú pháp cơ bản:&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code class="language-java" data-lang="java"&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="k"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;điều_kiện&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="c1"&gt;// Code thực hiện khi điều kiện đúng&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="2-câu-lệnh-if-else"&gt;2. Câu lệnh If-Else&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="cú-pháp"&gt;Cú pháp:&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code class="language-java" data-lang="java"&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="k"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;điều_kiện&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="c1"&gt;// Code khi điều kiện đúng&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="k"&gt;else&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="c1"&gt;// Code khi điều kiện sai&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="3-câu-lệnh-if-else-if-else"&gt;3. Câu lệnh If-Else If-Else&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="cú-pháp-1"&gt;Cú pháp:&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code class="language-java" data-lang="java"&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="k"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;điều_kiện_1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="c1"&gt;// Code khi điều kiện 1 đúng&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="k"&gt;else&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="k"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;điều_kiện_2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="c1"&gt;// Code khi điều kiện 2 đúng&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="k"&gt;else&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="c1"&gt;// Code khi tất cả điều kiện đều sai&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="4-câu-lệnh-switch-case"&gt;4. Câu lệnh Switch-Case&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Switch-case được sử dụng khi cần so sánh một biến với nhiều giá trị cụ thể.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Java Cơ Bản #3: Toán Tử và Biểu Thức</title><link>https://llhisme.github.io/post/java/java-co-ban-3/</link><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jan 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>lamlyhao453@gmail.com (Lâm Lý Hào)</author><guid>https://llhisme.github.io/post/java/java-co-ban-3/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="toán-tử-là-gì"&gt;Toán tử là gì?&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Toán tử&lt;/strong&gt; (Operator) là các ký hiệu đặc biệt được sử dụng để thực hiện các phép toán trên dữ liệu. &lt;strong&gt;Biểu thức&lt;/strong&gt; (Expression) là sự kết hợp của các biến, hằng số và toán tử.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="1-toán-tử-số-học-arithmetic-operators"&gt;1. Toán tử số học (Arithmetic Operators)&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;table&gt;
 &lt;thead&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;th&gt;Toán tử&lt;/th&gt;
 &lt;th&gt;Ý nghĩa&lt;/th&gt;
 &lt;th&gt;Ví dụ&lt;/th&gt;
 &lt;th&gt;Kết quả&lt;/th&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;/thead&gt;
 &lt;tbody&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;+&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;Cộng&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;5 + 3&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;8&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;-&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;Trừ&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;5 - 3&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;2&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;*&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;Nhân&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;5 * 3&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;15&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;/&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;Chia&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;10 / 3&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;3&lt;/code&gt; (chia nguyên)&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;%&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;Chia lấy dư&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;10 % 3&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;1&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;h2 id="2-toán-tử-gán-assignment-operators"&gt;2. Toán tử gán (Assignment Operators)&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;table&gt;
 &lt;thead&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;th&gt;Toán tử&lt;/th&gt;
 &lt;th&gt;Tương đương&lt;/th&gt;
 &lt;th&gt;Ví dụ&lt;/th&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;/thead&gt;
 &lt;tbody&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;+=&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;a = a + b&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;a += b&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;-=&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;a = a - b&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;a -= b&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;*=&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;a = a * b&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;a *= b&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;/=&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;a = a / b&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;a /= b&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;%=&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;a = a % b&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;a %= b&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;h2 id="3-toán-tử-so-sánh-comparison-operators"&gt;3. Toán tử so sánh (Comparison Operators)&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;table&gt;
 &lt;thead&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;th&gt;Toán tử&lt;/th&gt;
 &lt;th&gt;Ý nghĩa&lt;/th&gt;
 &lt;th&gt;Ví dụ&lt;/th&gt;
 &lt;th&gt;Kết quả&lt;/th&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;/thead&gt;
 &lt;tbody&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;==&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;Bằng&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;5 == 3&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;false&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;!=&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;Khác&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;5 != 3&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;true&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;Lớn hơn&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;5 &amp;gt; 3&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;true&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;Nhỏ hơn&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;5 &amp;lt; 3&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;false&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;&amp;gt;=&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;Lớn hơn hoặc bằng&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;5 &amp;gt;= 5&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;true&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;&amp;lt;=&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;Nhỏ hơn hoặc bằng&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;3 &amp;lt;= 5&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;true&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;h2 id="4-toán-tử-logic-logical-operators"&gt;4. Toán tử logic (Logical Operators)&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;table&gt;
 &lt;thead&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;th&gt;Toán tử&lt;/th&gt;
 &lt;th&gt;Ý nghĩa&lt;/th&gt;
 &lt;th&gt;Ví dụ&lt;/th&gt;
 &lt;th&gt;Kết quả&lt;/th&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;/thead&gt;
 &lt;tbody&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;&amp;amp;&amp;amp;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;VÀ (AND)&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;true &amp;amp;&amp;amp; false&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;false&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;`&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;`&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;HOẶC (OR)&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;!&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;PHỦ ĐỊNH (NOT)&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;!true&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;false&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;</description></item><item><title>Java Cơ Bản #2: Biến và Kiểu Dữ Liệu</title><link>https://llhisme.github.io/post/java/java-co-ban-2/</link><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>lamlyhao453@gmail.com (Lâm Lý Hào)</author><guid>https://llhisme.github.io/post/java/java-co-ban-2/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="biến-là-gì"&gt;Biến là gì?&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Biến&lt;/strong&gt; (Variable) là một &amp;ldquo;hộp&amp;rdquo; để lưu trữ dữ liệu trong chương trình. Mỗi biến có một tên và một kiểu dữ liệu cụ thể.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ví dụ đơn giản:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code class="language-java" data-lang="java"&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="kt"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;tuoi&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;25&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="c1"&gt;// Biến lưu số tuổi&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;String&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;ten&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;#34;Nam&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="c1"&gt;// Biến lưu tên&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="cách-khai-báo-biến"&gt;Cách khai báo biến&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="cú-pháp-cơ-bản"&gt;Cú pháp cơ bản:&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code class="language-java" data-lang="java"&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;kieuDuLieu&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;tenBien&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;giaTriKhoiTao&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="các-kiểu-dữ-liệu-cơ-bản"&gt;Các kiểu dữ liệu cơ bản&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="1-kiểu-số-nguyên"&gt;1. Kiểu số nguyên&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;table&gt;
 &lt;thead&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;th&gt;Kiểu&lt;/th&gt;
 &lt;th&gt;Kích thước&lt;/th&gt;
 &lt;th&gt;Phạm vi&lt;/th&gt;
 &lt;th&gt;Ví dụ&lt;/th&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;/thead&gt;
 &lt;tbody&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;byte&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;1 byte&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;-128 đến 127&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;byte tuoi = 25;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;short&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;2 byte&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;-32,768 đến 32,767&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;short nam = 2024;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;int&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;4 byte&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;-2 tỷ đến 2 tỷ&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;int luong = 15000000;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;long&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;8 byte&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;Rất lớn&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;long danSo = 97000000L;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;h3 id="2-kiểu-số-thực"&gt;2. Kiểu số thực&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;table&gt;
 &lt;thead&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;th&gt;Kiểu&lt;/th&gt;
 &lt;th&gt;Kích thước&lt;/th&gt;
 &lt;th&gt;Độ chính xác&lt;/th&gt;
 &lt;th&gt;Ví dụ&lt;/th&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;/thead&gt;
 &lt;tbody&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;float&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;4 byte&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;7 chữ số&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;float diem = 8.5f;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;double&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;8 byte&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;15 chữ số&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;code&gt;double pi = 3.14159;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;h3 id="3-kiểu-ký-tự-và-chuỗi"&gt;3. Kiểu ký tự và chuỗi&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;char&lt;/code&gt;: Lưu một ký tự duy nhất, ví dụ: &lt;code&gt;char kyTu = 'A';&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;String&lt;/code&gt;: Lưu một chuỗi ký tự, ví dụ: &lt;code&gt;String ten = &amp;quot;Java&amp;quot;;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 id="4-kiểu-logic"&gt;4. Kiểu logic&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;boolean&lt;/code&gt;: Chỉ có hai giá trị &lt;code&gt;true&lt;/code&gt; hoặc &lt;code&gt;false&lt;/code&gt;, ví dụ: &lt;code&gt;boolean daKetHon = false;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>Java Cơ Bản #1: Giới Thiệu Về Java và Cài Đặt Môi Trường</title><link>https://llhisme.github.io/post/java/java-co-ban-1/</link><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jan 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>lamlyhao453@gmail.com (Lâm Lý Hào)</author><guid>https://llhisme.github.io/post/java/java-co-ban-1/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="java-là-gì"&gt;Java là gì?&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Java là một ngôn ngữ lập trình hướng đối tượng được phát triển bởi Sun Microsystems (hiện thuộc Oracle) vào năm 1995. Java nổi tiếng với slogan &lt;strong&gt;&amp;ldquo;Write Once, Run Anywhere&amp;rdquo;&lt;/strong&gt; (Viết một lần, chạy mọi nơi).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id="tại-sao-nên-học-java"&gt;Tại sao nên học Java?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Phổ biến&lt;/strong&gt;: Java là một trong những ngôn ngữ được sử dụng nhiều nhất thế giới&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Đa nền tảng&lt;/strong&gt;: Code Java có thể chạy trên Windows, Mac, Linux&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cộng đồng lớn&lt;/strong&gt;: Có rất nhiều tài liệu và hỗ trợ từ cộng đồng&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cơ hội việc làm&lt;/strong&gt;: Nhiều công ty tuyển dụng lập trình viên Java&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;h2 id="cài-đặt-môi-trường-java"&gt;Cài đặt môi trường Java&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="bước-1-tải-và-cài-đặt-jdk"&gt;Bước 1: Tải và cài đặt JDK&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;JDK&lt;/strong&gt; (Java Development Kit) là bộ công cụ phát triển Java.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>